#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:54
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

# skip-rule: t-space
#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:56
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kdiskfree; displays the available file devices (hard drive partitions, "
"floppy and &CD; drives, USB sticks &etc;) along with information on their "
"capacity, free space, type and mount point. It also allows you to mount and "
"unmount drives and view them in a file manager."
msgstr ""
"<application>K‑disk‑prostor</application> prikazuje fajl uređaje (particije "
"hard‑diska, disketne i CD jedinice, USB štapiće, itd.) zajedno s podacima o "
"kapacitetu, slobodnom prostoru, tipu i tački montiranja. Takođe dopušta "
"montiranje i demontiranje jedinica i njihovo prikazivanje u menadžeru "
"fajlova."

# skip-rule: t-space
#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:61
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kdiskfree; is similar to the &systemsettings; Storage Devices module, but "
"takes up less screen space. It is useful if you want to keep a &kdiskfree; "
"window available at all times."
msgstr ""
"<application>K‑disk‑prostor</application> je sličan modulu skladišnih "
"uređaja u Sistemskim postavkama, ali zauzima manje mesta na ekranu. Koristan "
"je ako želite da prozor <application>K‑disk‑prostora</application> bude "
"stalno dostupan."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:69
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using &kdiskfree;"
msgstr "Korišćenje <application>K‑disk‑prostora</application>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:72
#, no-c-format
msgid "Starting &kdiskfree;"
msgstr "Pokretanje <application>K‑disk‑prostora</application>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Type <userinput><command>kdf</command></userinput> at a command prompt or "
"select <guimenuitem>KDiskFree</guimenuitem> from the <guisubmenu>System</"
"guisubmenu> group in the application launcher. The standard &Qt; and &kde; "
"command options are available, and can be listed by entering "
"<userinput><command>kdf</command> <option>--help</option></userinput> at the "
"command prompt."
msgstr ""
"Upišite <userinput><command>kdf</command></userinput> u komandni odzivnik "
"ili izaberite <guimenuitem>K‑disk‑prostor</guimenuitem> iz grupe "
"<guisubmenu>Sistem</guisubmenu> u pokretaču programa. Dostupne su standardne "
"KDE i Qt opcije naredbi, i mogu se nabrojati izvršavanjem "
"<userinput><command>kdf</command> <option>--help</option></userinput>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:81
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To run the application as an applet in the systemtray, use "
"<menuchoice><guisubmenu>System</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>KwikDisk</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> in application launcher."
msgstr ""
"Ako želite da program radi kao aplet u sistemskoj kaseti, idite na "
"<menuchoice><guisubmenu>Sistem</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>KwikDisk</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> u pokretaču programa."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The features of &kdiskfree; are also available in the &systemsettings; "
"module <guilabel>Storage Devices</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Mogućnosti <application>K‑disk‑prostora</application> dostupne su i "
"Sistemskim postavkama, modul <guilabel>Skladišni uređaji</guilabel>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:90
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Main window"
msgstr "Glavni prozor"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:92
#, no-c-format
msgid "The main &kdiskfree; window displays the available file devices."
msgstr ""
"Glavni prozor <application>K‑disk‑prostora</application> prikazuje dostupne "
"fajl uređaje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:94
#, no-c-format
msgid "Normally, the following pieces of information are included:"
msgstr "Normalno su prikazani sledeći podaci:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:96
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&kdiskfree; Screen</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>Ekran <application>K‑disk‑prostora</application>.</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:102
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&kdiskfree; Screen</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Ekran <application>K‑disk‑prostora</application>.</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:108
#, no-c-format
msgid "an icon depicting the type of storage"
msgstr "ikonica koja ukazuje na tip skladišta"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:109
#, no-c-format
msgid "device name"
msgstr "ime uređaja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:110
#, no-c-format
msgid "filesystem type"
msgstr "tip fajl sistema"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:111
#, no-c-format
msgid "total size"
msgstr "ukupna veličina"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:112
#, no-c-format
msgid "mount point"
msgstr "tačka montiranja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:113
#, no-c-format
msgid "free disk space"
msgstr "slobodan prostor"

# skip-rule: t-space
#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:114
#, no-c-format
msgid "the percentage of space used as a number and as a graph."
msgstr "procenat iskorišćenosti (kao broj ili grafikon)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:118
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<mousebutton>Left</mousebutton> clicking on the header of a particular "
"column sorts the devices according to that variable. A second "
"<mousebutton>left</mousebutton> click sorts in the opposite order."
msgstr ""
"<mousebutton>Levi</mousebutton> klik na zaglavlje kolone ređa uređaje prema "
"datoj promenljivoj. Naredni <mousebutton>levi</mousebutton> klik ređa "
"obrnutim redosledom."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:123
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Clicking with the &RMB; on a row pops up a menu. If that device is not "
"currently mounted, the <guimenuitem>Mount Device</guimenuitem> option is "
"available. If the device is mounted, it can be unmounted by choosing "
"<guimenuitem>Unmount Device</guimenuitem>. Selecting <guimenuitem>Open in "
"File Manager</guimenuitem> opens a new window with a graphical view of the "
"files on that device."
msgstr ""
"Desni klik na vrstu poziva meni. Ako dati uređaj trenutno nije montiran, tu "
"je opcija <guimenuitem>Montiraj uređaj</guimenuitem>. Ako uređaj jeste "
"montiran, može se demontirati izborom <guimenuitem>Demontiraj uređaj</"
"guimenuitem>. Stavka <guimenuitem>Otvori u menadžeru fajlova</guimenuitem> "
"otvara nov prozor sa grafičkim prikazom fajlova na tom uređaju."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:129
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The setting for the file manager used by &kdiskfree; is independent from the "
"choice in the &systemsettings; module <guilabel>Default Applications</"
"guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Postavka za menadžer fajlova u <application>K‑disk‑prostoru</application> "
"nezavisna je od one iz modula <guilabel>Podrazumevani programi</guilabel> u "
"Sistemskim postavkama."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:134
#, no-c-format
msgid "Menu Bar and Configuration"
msgstr "Traka menija i podešavanje"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:137
#, no-c-format
msgid "The File Menu"
msgstr "Meni <guimenu>Fajl</guimenu>"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:142
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycap>F5</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Update</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycap>F5</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Fajl</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Ažuriraj</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:147
#, no-c-format
msgid "Immediately updates the display to reflect the current status"
msgstr "Odmah ažurira prikaz tako da odražava tekuće stanje."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:153
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Quit</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>Ctrl</keycap><keycap>Q</"
"keycap></keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Fajl</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Napusti</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:160
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>Closes</action> &kdiskfree;"
msgstr "<action>Zatvara</action> <application>K‑disk‑prostor</application>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:164
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Additionally &kdiskfree; has some common &kde; <guimenu>Settings</"
#| "guimenu> and <guimenu>Help</guimenu> menu items, for more information "
#| "read the sections about the <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/ui.html#menus-"
#| "settings\">Settings Menu</ulink> and <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/ui."
#| "html#menus-help\">Help Menu</ulink> of the &kde; Fundamentals."
msgid ""
"Additionally &kdiskfree; has some common &kde; <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> "
"and <guimenu>Help</guimenu> menu items, for more information read the "
"sections about the <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-settings"
"\">Settings Menu</ulink> and <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus."
"html#menus-help\">Help Menu</ulink> of the &kde; Fundamentals."
msgstr ""
"<application>K‑disk‑prostor</application> takođe ima uobičajene KDE menije "
"<guimenu>Podešavanje</guimenu> i <guimenu>Pomoć</guimenu>. Detalje o njima "
"potražite u Osnovama KDE‑a, odeljci <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/ui."
"html#menus-settings\">meniju za podešavanje</ulink> i <ulink url=\"help:/"
"fundamentals/ui.html#menus-help\">meniju pomoći</ulink>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:173
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Settings Dialog"
msgstr "Dijalog postavki"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:176
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Configure &kdiskfree; Screen</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>Ekran za podešavanje <application>K‑disk‑prostora</application>."
"</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:182
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Configure &kdiskfree; Screen</phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>Ekran za podešavanje <application>K‑disk‑prostora</application>.</"
"phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:187
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This dialog has two tabbed windows, <guilabel>General Settings</guilabel> "
"and <guilabel>Mount Commands</guilabel>"
msgstr ""
"Ovaj dijalog ima dva prozora s jezičcima, <guilabel>Opšte postavke</"
"guilabel> i <guilabel>Naredbe montiranja</guilabel>."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:191
#, no-c-format
msgid "General Settings"
msgstr "Opšte postavke"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:191
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click on the word <guilabel>visible</guilabel> or <guilabel>hidden</"
"guilabel> to turn display of an data field on or off."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite na reč <guilabel>vidljivo</guilabel> ili <guilabel>skriveno</"
"guilabel> da uključite ili isključite polje podataka."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:193
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Change the update frequency by editing the value. The value in the box is "
"the interval (in seconds) between updates of the &kdiskfree; display to "
"reflect the current status."
msgstr ""
"Učestalost ažuriranja zadajete uređivanjem vrednosti perioda (u sekundama) "
"između ažuriranja prikaza <application>K‑disk‑prostora</application> tako da "
"odražava trenutno stanje."

# >! ui: File Manager --> ?
#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:196
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>File Manager</guilabel> setting controls the command executed "
"when the <guimenuitem>Open Filemanager</guimenuitem> popup menu item is "
"selected."
msgstr ""
"Postavka <guilabel>Menadžer fajlova</guilabel> navodi naredbu koju treba "
"izvršiti na izbor stavke <guimenuitem>Otvori u menadžeru fajlova</"
"guimenuitem> iz iskačućeg menija."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:199
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are also two check boxes. One controls if a file manager window will "
"be automatically opened when a device is mounted. The other causes an alert "
"window to pop up if a disk gets critically full."
msgstr ""
"Tu su i dve kućice. Jedna određuje da li će se prozor menadžera fajlova "
"automatski otvoriti kad se uređaj montira. Druga zadaje iskakanje prozora sa "
"upozorenjem ako se disk kritično prepuni."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:206
#, no-c-format
msgid "Mount Commands"
msgstr "Naredbe montiranja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:207
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Allows the user to specify the mount and unmount commands for a given "
"device, as well as the icon used to represent it. More information on these "
"commands can be found on the man page for <application>mount</application> "
"(type <userinput><command>man</command> <option>mount</option></userinput> "
"at the command prompt)."
msgstr ""
"Korisnik ovde može zadati naredbe za montiranje i demontiranje uređaja, kao "
"i ikonicu koja ga predstavlja. Više informacija o ovim naredbama može se "
"naći na uputnoj stranici <command>mount</command> (upišite "
"<userinput><command>man</command> mount</userinput> u komandni odzivnik)."

